<p>The relevant tithis for Ananda Marga fasting:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Ekádashii (11 days after new/full moon): occurs at angles 120° - 132° and 300° - 312°</li>
    <li>Amávasyá (New Moon): occurs at angles 348° - 360°</li>
    <li>Púrńimá (Full Moon): occurs at angles 168° - 180°</li>
</ul>

